## Workspace Map
```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}/                  — THE git repo (this folder = the main-branch checkout)
├── CLAUDE.md      — this file (identity + map + routing) · CONTEXT.md — worker dispatcher
├── .orchestrated  — marker: main is merge-only (activates the main-protection hook)
├── planning/      — FORWARD: todo.md (⏳ pending · planner-owned) · progress.md (🔄 in-progress board)
│                    · specs/srd · architecture · decisions/ (ADRs) · research/
├── memory/        — DURABLE record (native captures → curated up): primer.md · decisions.md
│                    · lessons.md · completed-tasks.md (✅ archive)
├── <code>         — production code + per-workspace CONTEXT.md; reaches main ONLY via PR merge
└── branches/<task>/ — gitignored per-task worktrees; work happens here
```

## Reporting Protocol
When a task is complete:
1. Run all validation commands — fix failures before reporting.
2. Summarize: what was done, what was tested, issues encountered, gotchas discovered.
3. Don't end the session without reporting back.
